metadata.name: Reviravolta
metadata.description:
Photograph taken on 2017.01.11 at Farol de Humaitá in Salvador-BA.

For a while the boys, who live nearby, jumped from the old Lighthouse.

These were days of lots of fun and games between them.

And, of course, lots of captures for us photographers.

Editing: 1/1.

The first collector will receive a print on 310g/m² cotton paper in size 60cm x 40cm, signed and numbered.

Printing of this work will not be permitted without the author's permission.
